REGENT HITECH PRIVATE LIMITED
description:
Regent Hitech Private Limited is an ISO 9001:2008 certified company engaged in manufacturing and supplying high quality Knife Gate Valves, Butterfly Valves, Ball Valves, Gate Valves, Globe Valves and Check Valves in India. We have established ourselves to cater to the industrial needs of leading Paper, Sugar, and Power & Chemical Industries. Established in 1994 as a Private Limited concern, our company is counted among prominent manufacturers and suppliers of industrial valves. Since 1974, we have been in the business of supplying various types of valves to these Industries through our sister concern. 

Since the inception, Regent Hitech Private Limited has grown in leaps and bounds and has won the confidence of all its customers by offering world-class products at competitive rates. Backed by sophisticated manufacturing facility in Industrial Area of NOIDA under Delhi / NCR, our company has successfully garnered a huge client base across the country. We are supported by diligent team of experts and knowledgeable support staff. RHPL is highly appreciated for quality products, flexible scheduling and prompt responses to inquiries. Our team works with complete dedication to develop components for specific needs also.
